{"entries":[{"id":"tsk-mat-16-4","title":"Matthew 16:4","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"MAT","chapterStart":16,"verseStart":4,"chapterEnd":16,"verseEnd":4},"content":"<p>If. 5:19,20,48; Ge 6:9; 17:1; Job 1:1; Ps 37:37; Lu 6:40; Php 3:12-15 go. 6:19,20; Mr 10:21; Lu 12:33; 14:33; 16:9; 18:22; Ac 2:45; 4:32-35 1Ti 6:17-19; Heb 10:34 come. 28; 4:19; 8:22; 9:9; 16:24; Mr 2:14; 8:34; 10:21; Lu 5:27; 9:23; 18:22 Joh 10:27; 12:26</p>"},{"id":"tsk-mat-16-9","title":"Matthew 16:9","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"MAT","chapterStart":16,"verseStart":9,"chapterEnd":16,"verseEnd":9},"content":"<p>we have forsaken. 4:20-22; 9:9; De 33:9; Mr 1:17-20; 2:14; 10:28; Lu 5:11,27,28; 14:33 Lu 18:28; Php 3:8 what. 20:10-12; Lu 15:29; 1Co 1:29; 4:7</p>"},{"id":"tsk-mat-16-14","title":"Matthew 16:14","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"MAT","chapterStart":16,"verseStart":14,"chapterEnd":16,"verseEnd":14},"content":"<p>he had. 13; Ex 19:5,6; De 5:27-30 a penny.\"The Roman penny is the eighth part of an ounce, which after five shillings the ounce is sevenpence halfpenny.\"</p>\n<p>18:28; 22:19; *margins Lu 10:35; Re 6:6 he sent. 1Sa 2:18,26; 3:1,21; 16:11,12; 1Ki 3:6-11; 18:12; 2Ch 34:3; Ec 12:1 Lu 1:15; 2Ti 3:15</p>"},{"id":"tsk-mat-16-19","title":"Matthew 16:19","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"MAT","chapterStart":16,"verseStart":19,"chapterEnd":16,"verseEnd":19},"content":"<p>when. 13:39,40; 25:19,31; Ro 2:6-10; 2Co 5:10; Heb 9:28; Re 20:11,12 unto. Ge 15:2; 39:4-6; 43:19; Lu 10:7; 12:42; 16:1,2; 1Co 4:1,2; Tit 1:7 1Pe 4:10</p>"},{"id":"tsk-mat-16-24","title":"Matthew 16:24","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"MAT","chapterStart":16,"verseStart":24,"chapterEnd":16,"verseEnd":24},"content":"<p>thine. 6:2,6,16; 2Ki 10:16,30,31; Eze 29:18-20; Lu 15:31; 16:25; Ro 3:4,19 I will. Joh 17:2</p>"}]}